# Microsoft.Agents.AI & Microsoft.Extensions.AI Package API Reference

## Project Dependencies
- **Microsoft.Agents.AI** v1.0.0 (ResearchAgent project)
- **Microsoft.Extensions.AI** (via Microsoft.Extensions.AI.Abstractions v10.4.1)
- **Microsoft.Extensions.AI.OpenAI** v10.4.1

---

## 1. CREATING AN AGENT - ChatClientAgent

### Namespace
`Microsoft.Agents.AI`

### Class: ChatClientAgent
Provides an `AIAgent` that delegates to an `IChatClient` implementation.

**CONSTRUCTORS:**

```csharp
// Constructor 1: Full manual configuration
public ChatClientAgent(
    IChatClient chatClient,
    string id,
    string name,
    string instructions,
    IList<AITool> tools,
    ILoggerFactory? loggerFactory = null,
    IServiceProvider? serviceProvider = null
)

// Constructor 2: Using ChatClientAgentOptions (preferred)
public ChatClientAgent(
    IChatClient chatClient,
    ChatClientAgentOptions options,
    ILoggerFactory? loggerFactory = null,
    IServiceProvider? serviceProvider = null
)
```

### Class: ChatClientAgentOptions
Configuration options for ChatClientAgent.

**PROPERTIES:**
- `string Id` - Agent identifier
- `string Name` - Agent name
- `string Description` - Agent description
- `string Instructions` - System instructions for the agent
- `IList<AITool> Tools` - Tools available to the agent
- `IChatHistoryProvider? ChatHistoryProvider` - Custom chat history provider
- `IEnumerable<AIContextProvider>? ContextProviders` - AI context enrichment providers
- `IEnumerable<MessageAIContextProvider>? MessageContextProviders` - Message enrichment providers
- `bool PersistChatHistory` (get/set) - Whether to persist chat history
- `string? ConversationIdPrefix` (get/set) - Optional prefix for conversation IDs

