## 5. AgentRunOptions & ChatClientAgentRunOptions

### Class: AgentRunOptions
Base run options for all agents.

**PROPERTIES:**
- `int MaximumIterations` (get/set) - Maximum number of iterations/turns (default may be unlimited)
- `TimeSpan? TimeLimit` (get/set) - Maximum time allowed for agent run
- Various context and history settings

### Class: ChatClientAgentRunOptions
Extended run options specific to ChatClientAgent, extends `AgentRunOptions`.

**CONSTRUCTORS:**
```csharp
public ChatClientAgentRunOptions()
{
}

public ChatClientAgentRunOptions(ChatOptions chatOptions)
{
}

public ChatClientAgentRunOptions(ChatClientAgentRunOptions other)
{
}
```

**PROPERTIES:**
- `ChatOptions? ChatOptions` (get/set) - Chat-specific options (temperature, max tokens, etc.)
- `Func<ChatClientAgentRunOptions, IChatClient>? ChatClientFactory` (get/set) - Factory to create/override IChatClient
- **INHERITED FROM AgentRunOptions:**
  - `int MaximumIterations` - Max iterations/turns
  - `TimeSpan? TimeLimit` - Max time limit

**METHODS:**
```csharp
public ChatClientAgentRunOptions Clone();
```

### Class: ChatOptions
Options for a chat request.

**CONSTRUCTORS:**
```csharp
public ChatOptions();
public ChatOptions(ChatOptions other);
```

**PROPERTIES:**
- `string? ConversationId` (get/set)
- `string? Instructions` (get/set) - Per-request instructions
- `double? Temperature` (get/set)
- `int? MaxOutputTokens` (get/set)
- `double? TopP` (get/set)
- `int? TopK` (get/set)
- `IList<AITool>? Tools` (get/set) - Tools for this request
- `ToolCallBehavior? ToolCallBehavior` (get/set)
- `Dictionary<string, object?>? AdditionalProperties` (get/set)

