## 8. CHAT MESSAGE TYPES

### Namespace
`Microsoft.Extensions.AI`

### Class: ChatMessage
Represents a message in a chat conversation.

**CONSTRUCTORS:**
```csharp
public ChatMessage()
{
    // Defaults to ChatRole.User
}

public ChatMessage(ChatRole role, string text)
{
}

public ChatMessage(ChatRole role, IList<AIContent> contents)
{
}
```

**PROPERTIES:**
- `ChatRole Role` (get/set) - User, Assistant, System
- `string Text` (get) - Concatenated text from all TextContent
- `IList<AIContent> Contents` (get) - Message contents (text, function calls, etc.)
- `string? MessageId` (get/set)
- `string? AuthorName` (get/set)
- `DateTimeOffset? CreatedAt` (get/set)
- `Dictionary<string, object?>? AdditionalProperties` (get/set)

